Interface List<E>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArrayList, LinkedList

    public interface List<E>
extends Collection<E>
    List interface is the child interface of Collection. It includes all the necessary basic methods for a simple list.
